title: Phish: Wisconsin Edition ("Alpine Valley 2010" bonus C
description:
Phish: Wisconsin Edition 


1. Tweezer (8/1/98) - 18:29

2. Down With Disease > (7/18/03) - 22:55

3. Catapult (7/18/03) - 2:41

4. Ghost > (8/9/97) - 15:31

5. Taste (8/9/97) - 10:01

6. Possum (6/26/04) - 10:20


This is the bonus CD that was packaged along with pre-orders of the "Alpine Valley 2010" boxset. This close to 80-minute collection (fully mastered) contains selections cherry-picked by Archivist Kevin Shapiro and was only available through Phish DryGoods. All songs are from past performances at Alpine Valley Music Theatre in East Troy, WI.
